-addition-end change-id="c2aa5750-5c27-4d7c-a065-dad18d9a0eb9"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="8763689" change-id="62f46192-361e-4398-9b12-4bf492518285" timestamp="1656533663819"?> network);</p></list-item><list-item id="id-94da163c-ad20-46ec-d252-1b288c421d3b"><p>sign charters and declarations of commitment in favour of gender equality;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-2f764757-1058-4e99-f19c-db8a91a014ed"><p>have an information system and internal statistical data broken down by gender;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-aaf9a877-b22e-4f67-963e-f682688e221b"><p>broadly use indexes and barometers containing gender-based indicators that can help to guide the actions taken in favour of equality.</p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="62f46192-361e-4398-9b12-4bf492518285"?></list-item></list><p/><p/></sec>